source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: normalize_help_output(&stdout)
---
Seek relative to current playback position or to an absolute time

Usage: spotuify seek [OPTIONS] <OFFSET>

Arguments:
  <OFFSET>  Seek target, e.g. +15s, -30s, 90s, or 2m

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format for the mutation receipt [default: table] [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
